cast.overview: Armed with only one word - Tenet - and fighting for the survival of the entire world, the Protagonist journeys through a twilight world of international espionage on a mission that will unfold in something beyond real time.
cast.title: Tenet

details.biography:
Ingrid Margus (born on January 5, 1994 in Tartu) is an Estonian actress.

She graduated from the Hugo Treffner Gymnasium in 2013, where she studied in the humanitarian class. Then she studied philosophy at Tallinn University for one year. In 2018, she graduated from the performing arts school of the Estonian Academy of Music and Theatre. In 2019, she completed her education at the Lee Strasberg Theater and Film Institute in New York.
details.name: Ingrid Margus
